    "description": "<p><strong>Style Passive:</strong> Your <strong>Attack Checks </strong>ignore Shields and 1/2 Cover, and you deal +1 damage against targets that are wielding a Shield or behind 1/2 Cover.</p><p><strong>Maneuver: (1 AP)</strong> You deal +1 damage, and the target makes a <strong>Physical Save </strong>to prevent dropping an Object it is holding or wielding (such as a Weapon, Shield, or other item).</p><p>The target has ADV if they are holding the object with 2 hands or they are larger than you. You cannot Disarm a creature that is 2 Sizes larger than you. If the target fails, the Object falls into a Space of your choice within 1 Spaces of the target.</p><p>Â </p><p><em><strong>System Tip: </strong>You can add Weapon Maneuvers as Weapon Enhacements for easier use. Just press \"Add Martial Maneuvers For Weapon\" on <strong>Enhancements </strong>tab on <strong>Item </strong>sheet.</em></p>",
